    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate validation against in-vitro hemolysis and velocity measurements across the full COU operating range. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all 5 operating points with validation uncertainty of 8.3%. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 scoping. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
